      <title>移民帮助美国就业增长速度超过鲍威尔的速度限制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/immigration-helps-us-jobs-grow-faster-than-powell-s-speed-limit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于移民增加，美国就业市场今年可能会再次大幅升温，超出美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔（Jerome Powell）认为的长期可持续水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/immigration-helps-us-jobs-grow-faster-than-powell-s-speed-limit</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
